<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7May1917"><font color="red">7 May 1917</font>, <cite>Pound/Joyce</cite> (Ezra Pound to Nora Joyce): I hope we&apos;ll be able to print &ldquo;Ulysses&rdquo; when finished. It could appear both in the &ldquo;Egoist&rdquo; and in the &ldquo;Little Review&rdquo; and J.J. would get double fees &hellip; I hope James will get through the beastly operation with all possible luck.</div>
